Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.53,0:00:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\b1\be1\fad(500,0)\pos(640,570)}5月7日　　晨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.30,0:00:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼喵　是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:29.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想问你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是奏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:36.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是什么早上好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别因为我父母都不在家　就理所应当地住进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.16,0:00:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.10,0:00:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然　昨天的那个不是做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了　脸色不太好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:00:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:02.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子叫了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生就是选择的连续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走上什么样的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都取决于自身的选择
